ime getting to know the people, the work, and the rhythm of the network before taking on a more formal role.","position":{"start":{"line":40,"column":1},"end":{"line":40,"column":1}},"key":"mo4Op3F44W"}],"key":"KgvGyYzC8T"},{"type":"div","children":[{"type":"mermaid","value":"flowchart TD\n    A[\"Interested in joining?\"] --> B[\"Join our Slack workspace\"]\n    B --> C[\"Attend community events\\nand meetings\"]\n    C --> D[\"Connect with the network team\"]\n    D --> E[\"Identify a lead contact\\nat your institution\"]\n    E --> F[\"Welcome aboard! 🎉\"]\n\n    style A fill:#fef3c7,color:#000,stroke:#fef3c7\n    style F fill:#fef3c7,color:#000,stroke:#fef3c7","key":"MQe8w6c5jy"}],"class":"mermaid-centered","key":"cG0239ZmPM"},{"type":"heading","depth":3,"position":{"start":{"line":59,"column":1},"end":{"line":59,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Start a conversation","position":{"start":{"line":59,"column":1},"end":{"line":59,"column":1}},"key":"fzsHxadUTm"}],"identifier":"start-a-conversation","label":"Start a conversation","html_id":"start-a-conversation","implicit":true,"key":"VKh5cGfXMe"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":61,"column":1},"end":{"line":61,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"When you’re ready to explore a closer connection to the network, get in touch:","position":{"start":{"line":61,"column":1},"end":{"line":61,"column":1}},"key":"pIOIn98Loc"}],"key":"Pgnd6XUuND"},{"type":"list","ordered":false,"spread":false,"position":{"start":{"line":63,"column":1},"end":{"line":65,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":63,"column":1},"end":{"line":63,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"strong","position":{"start":{"line":63,"column":1},"end":{"line":63,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Laura Langdon","position":{"start":{"line":63,"column":1},"end":{"line":63,"column":1}},"key":"OR6OGbH36p"}],"key":"FlThOFyNpW"},{"type":"text","value":", Community Manager: ","position":{"start":{"line":63,"column":1},"end":{"line":63,"column":1}},"key":"tVR21l8cz8"},{"type":"link","url":"mailto:lalangdon@ucdavis.edu","position":{"start":{"line":63,"column":1},"end":{"line":63,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"lalangdon@ucdavis​.edu","position":{"start":{"line":63,"column":1},"end":{"line":63,"column":1}},"key":"g8MsCW2Fle"}],"urlSource":"mailto:lalangdon@ucdavis.edu","key":"lkprhcUH06"}],"key":"jx9ZFseRM2"}],"key":"GRN7NlBuhS"},{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":64,"column":1},"end":{"line":65,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"strong","position":{"start":{"line":64,"column":1},"end":{"line":64,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Stephanie Lieggi","position":{"start":{"line":64,"column":1},"end":{"line":64,"column":1}},"key":"s2AZGPioga"}],"key":"TtMbTpy2zV"},{"type":"text","value":", Network Chair: ","position":{"start":{"line":64,"column":1},"end":{"line":64,"column":1}},"key":"kD98GaU8FD"},{"type":"link","url":"mailto:slieggi@ucsc.edu","position":{"start":{"line":64,"column":1},"end":{"line":64,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"slieggi@ucsc.edu","position":{"start":{"line":64,"column":1},"end":{"line":64,"column":1}},"key":"OjvbkJLhO4"}],"urlSource":"mailto:slieggi@ucsc.edu","key":"yNKHnPZ06X"}],"key":"Vfgv6W96bG"}],"key":"dHng5GCjAn"}],"key":"EZAYOOEsNQ"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":66,"column":1},"end":{"line":66,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"We’ll talk with you about what open source work looks like at your institution, what you’re hoping to get out of the network, and how we can support you.","position":{"start":{"line":66,"column":1},"end":{"line":66,"column":1}},"key":"FEbldnWW50"}],"key":"Tu8EJnpSlU"},{"type":"heading","depth":3,"position":{"start":{"line":68,"column":1},"end":{"line":68,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Identify a lead contact","position":{"start":{"line":68,"column":1},"end":{"line":68,"column":1}},"key":"xtJVVgtuDa"}],"identifier":"identify-a-lead-contact","label":"Identify a lead contact","html_id":"identify-a-lead-contact","implicit":true,"key":"YIXYlImwGy"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":70,"column":1},"end":{"line":70,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"As the relationship develops, we’ll ask your institution to identify a lead contact—someone who can serve as the primary point of connection between your institution and the network. This person doesn’t need to run an OSPO (not every member institution has one). They just need to be engaged with open source work and willing to participate in network activities.","position":{"start":{"line":70,"column":1},"end":{"line":70,"column":1}},"key":"YVG9Nyt30f"}],"key":"AKiCPfyVCa"},{"type":"heading","depth":3,"position":{"start":{"line":72,"column":1},"end":{"line":72,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Join the network","position":{"start":{"line":72,"column":1},"end":{"line":72,"column":1}},"key":"NdtBfMewHk"}],"identifier":"join-the-network","label":"Join the network","html_id":"join-the-network","implicit":true,"key":"HizxAX4nEe"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":74,"column":1},"end":{"line":74,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"From there, you’ll be welcomed into the network’s regular activities, including working groups and leadership discussions. The specifics of how new members are integrated into network governance are still evolving, and we’re committed to making the process transparent and collaborative.","position":{"start":{"line":74,"column":1},"end":{"line":74,"column":1}},"key":"BChmwgD5jc"}],"key":"pfoSKuvYv5"}],"key":"ade3GQy33Q"}],"key":"PE25pS7pUP"},"references":{"cite":{"order":[],"data":{}}},"footer":{"navigation":{"prev":{"title":"Network Services","url":"/about/services","group":"About"},"next":{"title":"Guiding Themes","url":"/about/guiding-